Shirye-shiryen Sainsbury's na bunkasa kasuwar kyan gani a Burtaniya
Sainsbury's ta sayi Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams, waɗanda ke da ma'aikata da yawa da suka ƙware a cikin hallways na shaguna da kyau.
