"Ina kokarin sanya kaina a wannan matsayi don samun kwallon kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna wasa a gaba sosai, don haka na yi kokarin ba da kaina duk lokacin da zai yiwu", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
