Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka saurari shaidar da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi takarar a kotun koli, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da wani cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi a shekarun 1980 a ranar Alhamis a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, siyasa ta ci gaba da tsayawa a kan hanya kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun katse shirin da suka saba da shi don sake watsa labarai na ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniya da Sanata Jeff Blake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da bincike kan zargin na mako guda.
