A lokacin da Kavanaugh ya ba da shaida, ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta wallafa a ranar Juma'a sun ga wannan labarin.
Kamfanin ya lissafa matsakaicin masu sauraro a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a nan take ba ne aka samu waɗannan lambobin ga sauran tashoshin da suka sake watsa shi, kamar su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da wasu matsaloli wajen ƙididdige yawan mutanen da suke kallon wani abu a ofishin.
