LeBron ya fara wasa da Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Fans da ke jiran ganin LeBron James ya fara wasan farko da Los Angeles Lakers na gab da ƙare.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan bude kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma, har yanzu ba a san minti nawa za ta buga ba.
Za a kara da daya kuma a kasa da 48, Walton ya ce a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Wani manema labarai na Lakers, Mike Trudell, ya wallafa a wani shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai iya buga 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan wani horo a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirye-shiryensa na wasanni shida na Lakers.
"A wannan mataki na rayuwata ba na bukatar wasannin da za su shirya ni", in ji shi.
Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da jerin taron neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wuraren da masu goyon baya suke, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da kuri'ar tabbatar da dan takararsa don rufe wurin da ake jiran Kotun Koli, Trump na neman samun tallafi don zaɓen rabin lokaci na gaba, saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar haɗarin rasa ikon Majalisar Dokoki lokacin da aka ajiye kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne da karfe 19:00 na daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi sharhi a kan halartar da ake yi a wannan makon na dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi ta daɗaitawa saboda zargin rashin halayyar jima'i kuma ya sa a jira a gaban majalisar dattawa don amincewa da shi har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken su.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
Haka kuma, yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump ya nuna cewa taron biyar na mako mai zuwa yana nufin ƙarfafa masu son kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da faɗaɗa rinjayen da suke riƙe a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a majalisar dokokin kasar tana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarin mulkinsa, wanda shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin da muke shiga yakin neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun Trump da bai so ya bayyana sunansa ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena Stadium a Wheeling a daren yau zai iya jawo hankalin masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma samun labarin a kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, kamar yadda West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya ci nasara da sama da maki 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, wanda ya koma baya a zaben.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi turawa a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: 'Yan wasan Amurka sun nuna cewa suna da ƙarfin hali don su ci gaba da fatan a gaban wasannin da za a yi a ranar Lahadi.
Bayan zaman guda uku, za a iya samun abin da wannan gasar ta Ryder ta bukata.
Ƙarfin motsa jiki mai juyawa ra'ayi ne na wasanni da aka ƙirƙira, amma 'yan wasa suna gaskata da shi sosai, musamman a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, ina ne za su ce ƙarfin yanzu?
"Mun samu maki shida a gabanmu kuma yanzu muna da hudu, don haka ina tsammanin za a iya la'akari da wannan karamin ci gaba", in ji Jordan Spieth a ƙarshen rana.
Turai ta ci gaba da samun maki hudu, da kuma wasu 12 a wasan.
Kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, 'yan Amirka sun ji cewa suna da iska a wurinsu kuma suna da dalilai masu yawa na yin farin ciki, da kuma wasu dalilai don ma'aurata da Spieth da Justin Thomas suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma suka sami maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai kisa daga shayi zuwa kore kuma yana yin wa'azi ta wurin misali.
Muryar muryar murya ta yi ta ƙara ƙarfi yayin da ya ci gaba da zagaye, yana shigar da wani muhimmin putt don daidaita wasan na huɗu yayin da shi da Thomas suka tafi biyu a ƙasa bayan ramuka biyu.
An samu irin wannan kukan da suka yi a ranar 15 ga watan Maris, daga masu watsa shirye-shiryen da suka ce sun yi imanin cewa Amurka ba ta fita ba tukuna.
"Abin da ya kamata a yi shi ne ƙara ƙoƙari kuma a mai da hankali ga wasan", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da waɗannan 'yan wasan suka yi.
Hatsarin da ya sa aka yi hakan ya kai 18 a cikin rami.
'Yan wasan da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin Ryder Cup.
Wannan ma'aurata na Turai suna da shekaru hudu daga cikin hudu kuma babu abin da zai iya faruwa da su.
Moliwood ita ce kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun kuma guji bogeys a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma ramin tara na ƙarshe na Jumma'a da safe.
Wannan tsananin tashin hankali da yadda suke samun karfin su a cikin jama'a masu saurin yi ya bayyana cewa wadannan su ne 'yan wasan da za a yi nasara da su a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za a samu wasu 'yan wasan da suka shahara kamar Fleetwood da Molinari ba don su yi alama ga yiwuwar nasarar Turai a lokacin da rana ta faɗi a Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau su yi aiki a lokaci guda a rami dabam dabam.
Duk da haka, har yanzu ba a yi magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun tura Sergio Garcia, gwarzon 'yan wasan kwallon kafa hudu na safe, bayan da ya yi aure da Alex Noren.
Wani mutum mai suna bogey da kuma wasu biyu a cikin ramin tara na farko sun binne Mutanen Espanya da kuma Yaren mutanen Sweden a cikin rami wanda ba su iya fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi ba za a samu wani taimako ba don fita daga cikin ramin.
Ƙwallon ƙafa da ƙwallon ƙafa suna da ban sha'awa don kallo a hankali domin suna godiya da hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba su bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun zai iya canzawa a cikin wani lokaci.
A yanzu dai, Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin tawagar kuma tana da babbar fa'ida a ranar ƙarshe, amma wannan taron na foursomes ya kuma nuna cewa tawagar Amurka ta yi ƙoƙari ta yi gwagwarmaya, wani abu da wasu, musamman Amurkawa, suka yi shakkarsa.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai ta tashi da kyau a ranar karshe ta Ryder Cup, bayan ta gama da fourballs da foursomes da sakamakon 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Ƙungiyar da ke da dalili mai suna Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci gwagwarmayar tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods wanda ya ga kansa cikin matsala, yana gaba da maki hudu a cikin matsayin Le Golf National.
Dan Turai Thomas Bjorn, yana kokarin kiyaye kofin da ya rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya mamaye wani tawagar Amurka wanda ya yi kuskure da yawa a lokacin wasannin safe, wanda ya ƙare 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin foursomes, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage nisa ba.
Dan wasan Amurka Jim Furyk yana bukatar ya samu maki takwas daga wasannin da aka buga a ranar Lahadi don ya ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon ɗan Turai na farko da ya ci maki huɗu a jere. Bugu da ƙari, shi da Molinari, waɗanda suka sami lakabi na Molliwood bayan ƙarshen mako mai ban mamaki, sune ma'aurata na biyu da suka ci maki huɗu a farkon wasanninsu huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin 'yan wasan hudu, haɗin gwiwarsu mai ban mamaki ya taimaka wajen doke Woods da kuma sabon ɗan Amurka Bryson Decahmbeau da ƙarfi 5-4.
Woods, wanda a wasannin Asabar biyu bai yi fice ba, ya yi wasu lokutan da ya yi fice, amma yanzu ya yi rashin wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 da ya yi a wasan hudu da hudu, da kuma wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya kasance yana hutawa don hudu na safe, ya sake zama abokin tarayya na Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu, yana doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, lambar farko da lambar uku ta duniya, bi da bi, da 2-1.
Ko da yake rana tana da kyau kuma tana da kwanciyar hankali a kudu maso yammacin Paris, Turai ba ta da kome.
Wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku, Jordan Spieth, da Justin Thomas sun yi amfani da su wajen yin magana da 'yan Amirka, inda suka samu maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun samu nasara mai ban sha'awa 2-1 a kan Ian Poulter da Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm a cikin huduballs sannan suka doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4-3 a cikin foursomes bayan sun rasa ramukan farko biyu.
A tarihin Ryder Cup, cewa wani tawagar ta dawo daga bambanci na maki hudu a wasanni guda biyu ne kawai ya faru sau biyu, ko da yake Furyk, a matsayin mai riƙe da trophy, yana buƙatar daidaituwa kawai don kiyaye shi.
Ko da yake sun kasance na biyu mafi kyau a cikin kwanaki biyu, amma yana da alama cewa yin wani counterattack a ranar Lahadi ya wuce your chances.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce babu wata dama da za su fara kashe makamai a gefe guda idan ba su da tabbaci
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ci gaba da takunkumin yana kara kara rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma babu wata dama da kasar ta ke da ita ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya a gefe guda a karkashin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya bayyana a gaban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki muhimman matakan kirki a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makaman nukiliya, rushe wuraren gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
Amma ba mu samu irin wannan amsa daga Amurka ba, in ji shi.
Idan ba mu amince da Amurka ba, ba za mu iya amincewa da tsaronmu na kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayin, babu wata dama mu fara kawar da makamai a gefe ɗaya.
Ko da yake Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafin Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya ta Washington ga tsarin hana makaman nukiliya ta mataki  wanda zai ba da lada ga kasar yayin da take yin matakai na mataki-mataki, sanarwa tana da muhimmanci, tun da bai ƙi da hana makaman nukiliya ɗaya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar bayan taron farko tsakanin wani shugaban Amurka mai aiki da wani shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a ranar 12 ga Yuni a Singapore, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don 'yancin nukiliya na yankin Koriya' kuma Trump ya tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi ƙoƙari ta kawo ƙarshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya kafin ta yi hakan.
Haka nan kuma, Washington ta yi tsayayya da kira don sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa a kan Koriya ta Arewa.
Ri ya ce: "Amurka ta nace da kawar da makaman nukiliya da farko kuma ta kara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi domin cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma da yin jayayya game da sanarwar kawo karshen yaki.
 Tunanin cewa hukuncin zai iya sa mu fāɗi a kan gwiwoyinmu ya zama abin ƙyama ga mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da tsauraran matakan zai ƙara sa mu ji tsoro.
Ri bai yi wani ambaton shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya sanar da shi a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ya nuna tarurrukan da Kim da shugaba Moon Jae suka yi a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kuma kara da cewa: "Idan Koriya ta Kudu ta kasance da sha'awar kawar da makaman nukiliya maimakon Amurka, kawar da makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba za ta kasance a cikin irin wannan halin da ake ciki ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa ne a kai harin da Koriya ta Arewa ta kai ga Amurka bayan da mummunan shugaban kasar Trump, a kan aikin kashe kansa, ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami".
A wannan shekarar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "dakatar da Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya", ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali a ci gaba da kawar da makamai, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da amfani da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da aka kafa don wannan: "Za mu iya ɗaukar shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar, ba kome ba".
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kamata ta saka wa Pyongyang a kan ci gaban da ta yi.
Duk da haka, kamar yadda Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka, Mike Pompeo, ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis: Tun da aka kafa takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya dole ne a ci gaba da bin doka da ƙarfi har sai mun tabbatar da cikakken tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya 
Majalisar Tsaro ta amince da takunkumi da za a yi wa Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006, a ƙoƙarin ta taƙaita kudade da za a ba wa manhajojin nukiliya da makaman nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya yi magana da Ri a wajen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma daga bisani ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ziyarar da ya yi a baya ba ta da kyau.
Ya bar birnin Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i kaɗan, Koriya ta Arewa ta ce 'yan bindigan ne suke bukatar hakan.
A wani taron da ta yi da Moon a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe wani wurin da ake amfani da makaman nukiliya da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta yi amfani da matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya sanar da shi cewa matakan da yake nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matakan daidaita dangantakarsa da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyar da yadda za su yi hutu sosai
Saboda sabon darasi da aka gabatar a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara, dukan daliban jami'a suna samun karin barci a kokarin su na yaki da al'adun maza da ke ci gaba da bunkasa na yin nazari a duk dare suna shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani farfesa ya gano cewa ɗaliban jami'a na farko a duniya ba su da wata ma'ana game da kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a likitancin barci a Makarantar Likitancin Harvard, da kuma wani masanin asibitin Brigham da Mata sun tsara wannan darasi, wanda aka yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ta samu dalilin da ya sa ta soma wannan darasin ne bayan ta yi jawabi game da yadda rashin barci ke shafar koyo.
A ƙarshen karatun, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa ta koyi wannan a yanzu, a cikin shekararta ta ƙarshe.
Ya ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya masa muhimmancin mafarki, wanda ya ba ni mamaki, in ji shi ga The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara yi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimman bayanai game da yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa wajen samun nasara a ilimi da wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyar jama'a.
Paul Barreira, malamin ilimin hauka a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard kuma darektan zartarwa na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun ne bayan ta gano cewa dalibai ba sa barci sosai a mako.
Wannan darasi na sa'a ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani sashe, akwai hoton ɗaki, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, takalma na wasanni da littattafai da ke gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, da kuma tasirin rashin barci a wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin kafa tsarin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon zuciya, hawan jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, wani gumin harabar da ke ɗauke da gumakan da ke nuna yadda ake tattaunawa ya ƙarfafa mahalarta su yi tunani game da rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa ba zai canja halayyar ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da hakkin su sani, kamar yadda kowa yake da hakkin ya san sakamakon shan taba a kan lafiyarsu, in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce al'adun alfahari da yin barci har yanzu suna nan, kuma ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba da ake yi wa ɗalibai na nufin cewa rashin barci yana da matsala.
Yin barci mai kyau da kuma barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama makamin sirri na ɗalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa; har ma don kauce wa yin nauyi, tun da rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta ji yunwa, don haka suna so su ci a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 a California da ke nazarin ilimin halittu da kimiyyar halitta, ya taimaka wa farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin bayan ya halarci ɗayan darussansa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe idanunsa kuma ya sa ya faɗaɗa makarantar.
Yana sa ran mataki na gaba shi ne a nemi dukan daliban digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga makarantar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi tunani game da saka ƙararrawa don su kwanta da kuma farkawa, kuma su san yadda hasken blue yake shafan allon na'urorin lantarki da na LED, wanda zai iya sa su yi rashin barci.
Livingston 1 - Rangers 0: Goal Menga ya binne mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sha wahala daga wani mummunan yanayi a waje da gida, lokacin da Dolly Menga ta kai hari ya kori kungiyar Steven Gerrard mai rauni zuwa ga 1-0 a Livingston.
Ibrox sun so su sami nasarar farko a waje tun daga nasarar 4-1 a watan Fabrairu a St. Johnstone, amma ƙungiyar Gary Holt ta doke Gerrard a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin koci, ta bar tawagar ta a maki takwas daga Hearts, shugabannin Ladbrokes Premiership.
Mene ne ya faru a lokacin da aka kai wa Menga hari?
Yanzu, Rangers sun sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku, a baya Hibernian ta hanyar bambancin raga.
Wataƙila 'yan wasan Rangers za su fuskanci ƙarin matsaloli, tun da alkalin layi Calum Spence ya sami taimakon likita saboda raunin kai bayan da aka ce wani ya jefa wani abu daga bayan mai baƙo.
Gerrard ya canza takwas daga cikin masu cin nasara da suka lashe wasan da Ayr, suna shiga wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin League na Scotland.
Holt ya fitar da 'yan wasan Livingston 11 da suka ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma ya yi farin ciki da yadda ƙungiyarsa ta yi nasara wajen kashe abokan hamayyarsa a kowane lokaci.
Wataƙila Rangers sun fi samun damar yin hakan, amma Livingston ya fi amfani da ƙwallon lokacin da ya samu.
Ya kamata su ci a minti biyu na farko, lokacin da Menga ya yi amfani da sararin samaniya don Scott Pittman wanda ya wuce tsakanin tsaron, ya bar shi kawai a gaban Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya tura ta waje.
Keaghan Jacobs ya yi kuskure mai zurfi ga Captain Craig Halket, amma abokin aikinsa a tsaron, Alan Lithgow, ya iya fitar da ita ta hanyar dogon sanda.
'Yan wasan Rangers sun sake samun iko, amma a karshe na uku, akwai karin bege fiye da tabbaci game da wasan su.
Babu shakka Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa an yi masa hukunci a minti na 15 na wasan, lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo, amma alkalin wasa Steven Thomson ya sa kunnuwansa suka kasa sauraron bukatar dan Colombia.
Rangers sun samu harbi biyu a cikin rabin farko, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, ya ga yana da wuya a magance ciwon kai na Lassana Coulibaly da kuma jefa Ovie Ejaria.
Ko da yake Livingston ya ci kwallo a minti na 34, amma ba wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan don ƙoƙarce-ƙoƙarcen da suka yi.
Har yanzu, Rangers sun kasa jimrewa da matakin da Jacobs ya ɗauka a kan wani babban mataki.
Scott Arfield bai yi ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya sanya kwallon ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai nutsuwa kuma ya ba Menga don ya ci kwallon.
A lokacin hutu, Gerrard ya maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent, wanda ya yi tasiri kusan nan take, tun da yake an ba da tayal ga Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya fita daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Duk da haka, Livingston ya ci gaba da kaiwa baƙi zuwa irin wasan da yake so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna share dogon wucewa bayan ɗaya.
Holt zai iya samun ƙarin fa'ida a cikin matakai na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya tsaya a kan ƙin Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya gama wani kusurwar kai wanda bai shiga ba.
Glen Middleton, mai maye gurbin Rangers, ya nemi fansa a ƙarshen wasan bayan ya yi gwagwarmaya da Jacobs, amma, Thomson ya sake duban wani bangare.
Almanac: Wanda Ya kirkiro Geiger Count
Kuma yanzu, shafi na Almanac na Sunday Morning: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka gabata, kuma KARANTA... an haifi mai zuwa mai ilimin lissafi Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya don ganowa da kuma auna radiation, wani kirkiro da ya kawo karshen na'urar da aka sani da Geiger counter.
Mai lissafi Geiger, wanda tun daga wannan lokacin ya zama ginshiƙi na kimiyya, ya zama ginshiƙi na al'adun pop, kamar a cikin fim din Bells of Coronado, na 1950, tare da 'yan wasan kwaikwayo Roy Rogers da Dale Evans a cikin ayyukan da ba su dace ba na masana kimiyya:
Mutum:  Menene wannan?
Rogers:  Yana da ma'aunin Geiger, ana amfani dashi don gano ma'adinai masu radiyo, kamar uranium.
Sa'ad da ka saka belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin raƙuman ruwa da ake fitarwa daga ma'adinai.
Evans: "Yana kama da rediyo!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a 1945, lokacin da yake kusan cika shekaru 63.
Amma abin da ya faru da sunan shi yana da rai.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ya ga ƙwayoyin cuta
Wani sabon allurar rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ya ga ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ya kashe su.
A matsayin wani ɓangare na magani, allurar tana koya wa tsarin rigakafi ya gane ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wannan aikin yana bukatar a cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya kuma a canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Saboda haka, za su iya samun furotin da yake da yawa a cikin cututtukan daji kuma su sake yin amfani da shi.
Wani gwaji na allurar yana samar da sakamako mai kyau ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da ciwon daji daban-daban.
Wata mace da aka yi wa allurar rigakafi, wadda ke koya wa tsarin rigakafi ya gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga yadda cutar kansa ta ƙuƙwalwa ta tafi har tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan aikin yana bukatar a cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin mai haƙuri kuma a canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su iya ganin furotin da ake kira HER2 wanda yake da yawa a cikin ciwon daji, sannan a sake yin amfani da ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Bincikenmu ya nuna cewa muna da alurar riga kafi mai ban al'ajabi.
Farfesa Berzofsky ya ce, HER2  yana sa ciwon daji ya yi girma a wasu nau'o'in daji kamar nono, ovari, huhu, ko kuma ciwon daji na baya.
Wani tsarin da ya yi kama da na karɓar ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya kuma ya koya musu su kai wa ƙwayoyin cuta hari ya yi aiki a maganin cutar sankarar ƙwayar cuta.
