Kit Harington, tauraruwar Wasannin Daukaka, ta kai hari ga namiji mai guba
Kit Harington ya shahara saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin jerin tashin hankali na HBO na wasan kwaikwayo na tsohuwar zamani, Game da kursiyai.
Dan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi ta kaiwa jarumin da ya yi wa'azi a matsayin jarumi, yana cewa, irin waɗannan ayyukan a kan allon suna sa matasa su kasance masu tsananin hali don a girmama su.
A wata hira da aka yi da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin wani abu ya tafi daidai ba kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri abokin aikinsa a Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana ganin yana da mahimmanci ya magance wannan batun.
"Na ga yana da muhimmanci a yanzu, ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?"
Mene ne muka koya wa maza yayin da suke girma, muna tunanin matsalolin da muke gani a yanzu?
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya ɗaukar nauyin wani ɓangare na ƙaruwar namiji mai guba saboda halayensu na namiji.
Ya ci gaba da cewa: "Mecece halitta, kuma me ake koyarwa?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a titi, da ya sa matasa su ji cewa dole ne su kasance irin wannan mutum?
Ina ganin wannan na daga cikin manyan tambayoyin zamaninmu. Ta yaya za mu canza shi?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa wani abu ya ɓace a cikin ilimin matasa.
A cikin hira, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai shiga cikin kowane prequel ko sequel na Game da kursiyai ba lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a lokacin rani mai zuwa, yana mai cewa yana da "kwani daga fagen yaƙi da dawakai".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai taka rawa a True West, wasan kwaikwayo na Sam Shepard wanda ya ba da labarin wani mai samar da fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ɓarawo ne.
A kwanan nan, actor ya bayyana cewa yana ganin sanin matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya samu daga Game of Thrones.
"Na san matata a cikin wasan kwaikwayon, don haka a wannan ma'anar, ta ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata daga yanzu", in ji ta.
Rose ta wakilci Ygritte, sha'awar ƙaunar mutumi na Kit, Jon Snow, a cikin jerin abubuwan ban mamaki na Emmy Award.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a wani gonar Leslie ta iyali, a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karin kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin cututtuka
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS zai karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
A kasar akwai mutane fiye da 820,000 da suka kamu da cutar, a cewar hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kadai, an samu wasu sabbin mutane 40,000.
Mafi yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar sun kamu da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya kawo canji a kan abin da ya faru a baya.
A al'adar, cutar HIV ta bazu cikin sauri a wasu sassan ƙasar Sin sakamakon ƙarin jini da aka yi wa wanda ya kamu da cutar.
Amma, yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya ragu sosai, kamar yadda hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka bayyana a wani taro da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
A kowace shekara, yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin na ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An yi watsi da jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma an nuna wariya sosai ga kungiyar LGBT.
Domin ra'ayin da kasar ta nuna, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da wasu maza za su auri mata.
