Johnny English: "An sake yin aiki".
Yanzu ya zama al'ada a nemi 'yan ta'adda na Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da ra'ayi na Burtaniya. da alama wannan shine abin da ya dace a yi tare da wannan sabon sashi na aikin parody da wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya dawo rayuwa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Returns.
Shin wannan ba'a ce ta kai tsaye game da yadda muke da ban mamaki cewa mu ne sabuwar damar fitarwa ta al'umma?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English, wanda ba shi da iko, da idanunsa masu tsalle da fuskarsa mara magana, ya sabunta lasisinsa na shiga cikin kafa a karo na biyu.
Hakika, shi ne wannan jami'in asirin da ba shi da kyau wanda, duk da cewa yana da wasu abubuwan da ba su da kyau na lalata sha'awa, yana da ɗan Clouseau, wani ɗanɗano na Mr. Bean da kuma ɗanɗano na wannan mutumin wanda ya buga ƙamus guda ɗaya a kan batun Motocin Wuta wanda aka buga a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Bugu da ƙari, asalinsa ya dogara ne akan mutum mai ba da labari mai ban mamaki da kuma na duniya wanda Atkinson ya wakilci shekaru da yawa da suka gabata a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta da su, yana shuka rikici a bayansa.
A wannan sashe na ƙarshe, akwai lokaci ɗaya ko biyu masu kyau.
Na yi farin cikin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa kusa da wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da ya sa rigar ƙarni na dā yayin da haikalin ya yi ta halaka jirgin.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki ta yi fice, amma yanayin da yake da ɗan gajeren lokaci kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman yanzu da 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suka ƙara kayan wasan kwaikwayo ba tare da matsala ba.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a ganina, rashin jin daɗin Johnny English ba shi da wayo da kuma hikima kamar Atkinson's silent jokes a matsayin Mr. Bean.
Yanzu, da maimaitawa da ake yi a yau shi ne cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar leken asiri ta Birtaniya, yana bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an da ke aiki a cikin damuwa game da jami'in da ke aiki, wani abu mai ban tausayi ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya cika ministan firaministan kasar, wani mutum mai girma da kuma tsinkaye wanda ke kallon yadda shahararsa ta siyasa ke raguwa: Emma Thompson ta yi iyakar ƙoƙarinta a cikin wannan mutum wanda kusan kamar Theresa May ne, amma rubutun bai bar wani wuri mai yawa don aiki ba.
Masu ba da shawara a fannin leken asirinsa sun gaya masa cewa tun da yake dukan 'yan leken asirin da ke aiki suna cikin haɗari, dole ne ya nemi wanda ya bar aikin.
Wannan dole ne ya zama Johnny English, wanda yanzu yake koyarwa a makarantar banza, duk da cewa yana koyar da darussan asiri game da yadda ake zama jami'in asiri: akwai wasu kyawawan barkwanci, tun da yake makarantar leken asiri ce kamar makarantar rock.
An tura English zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake wakilta.
Yanzu, Bough mutum ne da ya auri wani kyaftin jirgin ruwa, wani muhimmin rawa wanda ba a amfani da Vicki Pepperdine sosai ba.
Don haka, Batman da Robin da ke yin mummunan aiki a cikin Sirrin Mai Girma sun koma aiki, tare da kyakkyawan matar fatal Ophelia Bulletova, wanda Olga Kurylenko ya wakilta.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista tana fada cikin hannun wani mai kudi da yawa a duniyar fasaha wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta, mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya cikin yanayi mai ban mamaki: sun yi suturar hidima, sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai kyau, sun ɓoye rikici a cikin jirgin ruwan Volta mai daraja; kuma, English ya zama lalataccen lalata yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da kwalkwali na gaskiya na gaskiya don sanin ciki na gidan Volta.
Hakika, an yi amfani da su sosai a wannan fim ɗin, amma duk da cewa suna da ban dariya da kuma ban dariya, duk da haka, suna ba da ɗan ɗan ƙaramin ji.
Kayan da ya dace sosai.
Kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, na yi mamakin ko masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson wani rawar da za ta yi gaskiya ga baiwarsa.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta yi musun cewa tana shirin sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, amma suna karbar biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi tunanin wani shiri mai zurfi wanda Britaniyawa za su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma za su biya biyar.
A cewar jam'iyyar, masu mallakar kamfanoni suna son su ba ma'aikata kuɗin da suka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha ta wucin gadi, ta ba su karin ranar hutu.
A sakamakon haka, ma'aikata za su yi kwana uku a ƙarshen mako don samun albashin da aka biya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai dace da tsare-tsaren jam'iyyar da kuma tsarin tattalin arziki na neman ma'aikata a kasar.
Wannan sauyawar zuwa mako na kwana hudu ya samu goyon bayan Majalisar Tarayyar Tarayyar Turai, domin hanya ce ta ma'aikata su amfana daga tattalin arzikin da ke canjawa.
Kamar yadda wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labor ya fada wa The Sunday Times: Ana sa ran sanarwar sake duba hukumar kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba za a samu ba daga rana zuwa rana, amma makon aiki na kwanaki hudu tabbas batun ne da jam'iyyar ke fatan shigarwa don sake daidaita tattalin arzikin a madadin ma'aikaci, da kuma cikin tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar".
Jam'iyyar Labor ba za ta kasance ta farko ba wajen tallafawa irin wannan ra'ayin, tun da Jam'iyyar Green ta riga ta yi alkawarin mako na aiki na kwanaki hudu a yakin neman zaben kasar ta 2017.
Amma a yanzu, ba duk 'yan Labour ne ke goyon bayan wannan shawarar ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun Labour ya ce: "Matsayin aiki na kwana hudu ba na siyasa ba ne a jam'iyyar kuma ba za a tattauna shi a wannan lokacin ba".
Ministan kudade mai duhu, John McDonnell, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour da aka gudanar a makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa na kawo juyin juya halin zamantakewa a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce yana son ya samu ikon "shugabannin da ba a san su ba" da kuma "masu amfani da su" a kan kamfanonin da ke ba da sabis na gwamnati.
Shirin da ministan ya yi na cewa masu ruwa da ruwa ba za su samu cikakken hannun jari ba, tun da gwamnatin Labour za ta iya yin amfani da kudade da suka dace da rashin daidaito da aka samu.
