Menene bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya? Shin ya yi nasara wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai yi bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara na Global Citizen Festival, inda za a taru da wata babbar ƙungiyar taurari don yin wani aiki mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A wannan shekara, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga yadda dubban dubban mutane za su yi tafiya zuwa babban Lawn na Central Park don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon kamar na Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron: kawar da talauci mai tsanani a 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, kungiyar wayar da kan jama'a ta duniya da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da ta.
Idan kana son samun shiga kyauta don taron (sai dai idan za ka iya biyan VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon sun yi jerin ayyuka ko aiki, kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko wani abu da zai taimaka wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin da suke da shi na kawar da talauci.
Amma menene Global Citizen ta cim ma bayan shekara 12 da ta kai ga burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta rinjayar mutane su dauki mataki ko kuma kawai wani nau'i ne na abin da ake kira "cluttivism", wanda ya kira matsayin da muke ɗauka lokacin da muke tunanin muna yin wani abu mai amfani da gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan buƙatun kan layi ko aikawa da tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" na magoya bayanta don tallafawa manyan manufofi daban-daban.
Ta wajen yin hakan, sun ce sun sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37, kuma hakan zai shafi rayukan mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawuran da aka yi 390 da kuma sanarwar da suka fito daga hannun jarinta, daga cikinsu, an riga an kashe ko an tara akalla dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka ba su sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Daga cikin manyan alkawuran akwai "The Power of Nutrition", wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu aiwatar da ayyukan da ke Burtaniya tare da haɗin kai tare da haɗin kai don "taimaka yara su girma da haɓaka da cikakken damar su". Don haka, an ba da shawarar samar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa kawo ƙarshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan karɓar tweets sama da 4,700 daga masu ba da gudummawa na Global Citizens.
"Godiya ga goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa, da kuma abokan haɗin gwiwar Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya yin wani ƙaramin ci gaba a tarihin rashin adalci na zamantakewar rashin abinci mai gina jiki, Tracey Ullman, jakadan 'The Power of Nutrition,' ta gaya wa taron a lokacin wani taro a watan Afrilu na 2018 a London.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan ta gudanar da ayyuka sama da 5000 don inganta abinci mai gina jiki a Birtaniya ga iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da kudaden wani shiri, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai taimaka wa mata da yara miliyan 5 su amfana daga ayyukan da suka shafi abinci mai gina jiki.
