Tun da yake 'yan Republican da yawa suna neman neman neman takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh a gaban zargin cin zarafin jima'i, masu bincike sun yi gargadin cewa za a iya samun koma baya, musamman ga mata, a cikin kuri'un da za su gudana a tsakiyar majalisa.
