Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya yana tunanin fara sabon intanet don yin gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, yana kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani wanda yake kokarin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Inrupt shine sabon aikin da ya fi dacewa da fasahar zamani, wani kamfani wanda ya dogara da dandamali na Berners-Lee na Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su sami damar yin amfani da wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya ya ce manufar da ke bayan Inrupt ita ce "mulki da duniya".
"Ya kamata a yanzu", ya ce game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don masu amfani su iya ƙirƙirar nasu "takarda bayanan sirri ta kan layi" ko POD.
Yana iya ɗauke da jerin abubuwa, jerin ayyukan da ba a yi ba, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike kuma a lokaci guda.
Wani abu da ke da ban sha'awa game da adana bayanan sirri a kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne ke yanke shawarar gaba ɗaya wanda zai iya samun dama ga wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "koyarwar mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar babban daraktan kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce ta haɗa albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewar da suka dace don Solid ya isa ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu daga cikin masu haɓaka waɗanda aka haɗa da su waɗanda aka ɗauke su don aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shiryen son rai.
Daga wannan makon, masu ci gaba da fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za su gabatar da canji mai zurfi inda dukkanin tsarin kasuwancin su za a gyara su gaba daya daga rana zuwa rana.
"Ba za mu nemi izini ba".
A wani rubutu a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta game da Inrupt cewa "aikinta shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka kirkira a Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya (W3C) a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Duk da cewa yana ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
