Taron Trump da Rosenstein na iya sake jinkirta, a cewar Fadar White House
Taron babban hadarin Donald Trump da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein na iya "dakatar da wata mako", yayin da ake ci gaba da jayayya game da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke bincika tsoma baki a zaɓen Rasha, alaƙa tsakanin taimakon Trump da Rasha, da yiwuwar hana shugaban ƙasa yin adalci.
Binciken ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauya ko a'a kuma, ta haka, ya sa mu'amala da 'yancin kai na Mueller ya ci gaba da jan hankalin Washington har tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya rubuta tattaunawar da ya yi da Trump ta hanyar makirufo da shi kansa ya sa don ƙoƙarin sauke shugaban ta hanyar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya ƙaryata cewa gaskiya ne.
Duk da haka, a ranar Litinin da ta gabata ya tafi fadar White House, a tsakanin labarai inda aka ce yana gab da yin murabus.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da ganawa da Trump (wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York) a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce zai "fi son ba" ya sallami Rosenstein amma an dage taron ne don kauce wa rikici da kotun shari'a ta Majalisar Dattawa ta Amurka inda Kavanaugh da wata mace da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya nemi FBI ta bincika zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh na tsawon mako guda, ko da yake hakan zai jinkirta zaben majalisar dattawa.
Sakataren yada labarai na Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a ranar Lahadi a Fox News.
Lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da taron Rosenstein, ya ce: "Ba a sanya wani kwanan wata ba, zai iya zama wannan makon ko kuma a jinkirta wani, la'akari da duk abin da ke faruwa tare da Kotun Koli.
Za mu yanke shawara a kan abin da ya faru kuma zan sanar da manema labarai, kamar yadda na saba yi".
Wasu 'yan jarida za su musanta wannan ikirarin: Sanders bai gudanar da wani taron manema labarai a fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga Satumba.
Mai gabatar da taron Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa na yi hakan.
Sanders ya ce rashin taron manema labarai ba don ƙiyayya da 'yan jaridar TV da ke yin magana ba, ko da yake ya ce: "Ba zan yi jayayya da cewa suna yin fariya ba".
Daga nan sai ta nuna cewa, za a kara samun lamba tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
"Shugaban kasa ya yi taro da amsoshi fiye da duk wani shugaban kasa da ya yi a baya", in ji shi, yayin da yake ba da hujja ba: "Mun yi tsayayya da waɗannan lambobin".
Sanders ya ce za a ci gaba da yin taron manema labarai, amma "idan manema labarai suna da zaɓi na tambayar shugaban Amurka kai tsaye, ina ganin ya fi kyau su yi mini.
Mun yi kokarin yin hakan sau da yawa kuma kun ga muna yin hakan sau da yawa a cikin makonni da suka gabata, don haka wannan zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai lokacin da za ku iya magana da shugaban Amurka".
Trump yakan amsa tambayoyi a lokacin da ya bar fadar White House ko kuma lokacin da ya halarci taron jama'a ko taron manema labarai tare da manyan jami'an da suka ziyarce shi.
Tattaunawa da shi a taron manema labarai ba sa faruwa sosai.
A gaskiya ma, a wannan makon a birnin New York, shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa hakan ya faru, inda ya yi wani bayyanar da ba ta da kyau, kuma a wasu lokatai kuma baƙon abu, ga 'yan jarida da suka taru a wurin.
