Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'an sun ce, ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da aka toshe hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an bayar da taimako ba su samu wani bayani daga hukumar Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da wurin girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kusa da ƙarshen wani kusurwar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mazaunan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regencia, wanda yanki ne na gudanarwa wanda ya fi lardin ƙasa, yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Fishing da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana kuma yin amfani da nickel a lardin, amma ana yin amfani da shi sosai a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunami ya shafi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami kuma ya afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin Yankin Wuta na Tekun Fasifik, yanki mai yawan girgizar ƙasa, kuma tana yawan girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai girma a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, ya haifar da tsunami a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya. Fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu sun faru a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afkawa yammacin bakin teku na Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An samu dubban mutane a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi gabar tekun kudu, tare da mutuwar kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi ya afkawa mulkin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, yana haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin tunawa da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, ba a yi tsunami ba, amma fashewar gine-gine ta kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Tsibirin Lombok (Indonesia) ya yi girgizar ƙasa mai girma wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun rasa gidajensu na ɗan lokaci.
An kama ɗansa na farko da ake zargi da tashin hankali a gida
Track Palin, babban dan tsohuwar gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne bisa zargin yin tawaye.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, dan garin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin yin ta'addanci a gida, ta hanyar tsoma baki a cikin rahoton ta'addanci a gida da kuma tsayayya da kama shi, a cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton ya ce, sa'ad da wata saninsa ta yi ƙoƙari ta kira 'yan sanda don su yi magana game da laifin da ake zargi, sai ya ƙwace wayar.
An yanke hukuncin tsare Palin a gidan yari na Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an tsare shi da asusu na dala 500, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa ba shi da laifi a lokacin da aka nemi ya bayyana kansa, in ji gidan.
Palin tana fuskantar manyan laifuka guda uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin za ta iya yin shekara guda a kurkuku kuma ta karɓi tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma zarge shi da aikata laifi na ƙarami na aji na B, wanda zai iya kai ga kurkuku na kwana ɗaya da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge ta da zaluntar mahaifinta, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton abin da ake zargi da kai hari.
A halin yanzu, ana sauraron shari'ar a gaban kotun tsofaffin sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da cin zarafin gida, da tsoma baki a cikin rahoton aikata laifukan tashin hankali na gida da kuma mallakar makami a cikin yanayin buguwa, dangane da lamarin.
Abokinsa ya ce ya yi masa dūka a fuska.
Wasu kungiyoyin tsofaffi sun soki Sarah Palin a shekarar 2016 saboda danganta halin tashin hankali na ɗanta da rashin lafiyar post-traumatic stress disorder wanda ya samo asali daga hidimarta a Iraki.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Mutane Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a da ta gabata.
Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta jawo tsunami kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
Cibiyoyin sadarwa da wutar lantarki sun fadi kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta faru ne kusa da tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin Indonesia.
Akwai bidiyon da ke yawo a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin da aka yi hakan.
Dubban mutane sun taru don bikin bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya kai ga bakin teku.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa musamman ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, wanda ba a yi masa hukuncin kisa ba a jihar saboda laifin tarayya tun 1953.
An ce Saipov mai shekara 30 ya yi amfani da wata motar hayar Home Depot don kai hari a wata hanyar keke a West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba da ya gabata, inda ya rushe masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke da ke kan hanyarsa.
Don a yi musu hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe 'yan mata takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni, bisa ga sanarwar da aka gabatar a Kananan Hukumomin New York.
Ana iya yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan tuhuma biyu, a cewar takardar shari'a.
Makonni da yawa bayan harin, babban juriyar tarayya ta gabatar da Saipov da tuhuma na zargin 22 wanda ya hada da tuhuma takwas na kashe-kashe tare da taimakon aikata laifuka, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a cikin waɗannan shari'o'i, da kuma tuhuma na tashin hankali da lalata motocin mota.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci a yi shiri sosai kuma a yi tunani sosai, wanda suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin mai "m, mai zalunci da lalata".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar iyalan da abokai Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, an ƙayyade a cikin sanarwar niyya.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance masu yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Shekara goma da ta shige tun lokacin da Kudancin Yankin New York ya yi shari'ar kisa.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A karo na karshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York shine Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a 1953. An kashe wannan auren bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu kafin.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu a cikin kujera na lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar zargin, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya yi amfani da bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa don kai harin.
Ya kuma nemi a ɗaga tutar ISIS a ɗakinsa na asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya bayyana kansa da laifinsa a kan zargin da ake masa na 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun "bayyana rashin jin dadin" da hukuncin da kotun ta yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar wata sanarwa ta laifi da hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai kara yawan abin da ya faru ga duk mutanen da ke ciki", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare hakkin Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
